how to create beautiful, visually-rich graphics using the canvas view, materials, and enhancements to symbols. Explore multi-column tables on macOS, refinements to focus and keyboard interaction, and the multi-platform search API. And we‚Äôll show you how to take advantage of features like Swift concurrency, a brand new AttributedString, format styles, localization, and so much more."}],"kind":"article","role":"sampleCode"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC21-10197-Discover-and-curate-Swift-Packages-using-Collections":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc21-10197-discover-and-curate-swift-packages-using-collections","kind":"article","title":"Discover and curate Swift Packages using Collections","abstract":[{"text":"Whether you‚Äôre curating packages for your team, for education purposes, or to share with other developers, Swift Package Collections can help you discover, explore and import new packages into your project. Discover improvements in the Swift Package workflow using Collections, and learn how you can curate, create, sign, and share your own Swift Package Collections.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC21-10197-Discover-and-curate-Swift-Packages-using-Collections","role":"sampleCode"},"https://github.com/apple/swift-evolution/blob/be686706919cab796b47b8c528a1fa52028a8335/proposals/0293-extend-property-wrappers-to-function-and-closure-parameters.md":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/apple\/swift-evolution\/blob\/be686706919cab796b47b8c528a1fa52028a8335\/proposals\/0293-extend-property-wrappers-to-function-and-closure-parameters.md","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/apple\/swift-evolution\/blob\/be686706919cab796b47b8c528a1fa52028a8335\/proposals\/0293-extend-property-wrappers-to-function-and-closure-parameters.md","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SE-0293"}],"title":"SE-0293"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/rayfix":{"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/